trans-unit.source: Represents an ordered collection of <see cref="T:System.Windows.UIElement" /> child elements.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção ordenada de elementos filho <see cref="T:System.Windows.UIElement" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Panel> base class uses a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.UIElementCollection> to represent its collection of child elements.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Panel> usa classe de base um <xref:System.Windows.Controls.UIElementCollection> representar sua coleção de elementos filho.

trans-unit.source: Methods and properties defined by the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.UIElementCollection> affect all objects derived from <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Panel> and define a common feature-set for the manipulation of <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Panel> child elements.
trans-unit.target: Métodos e propriedades definidas pelo <xref:System.Windows.Controls.UIElementCollection> afetam todos os objetos derivados de <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Panel> e definir um conjunto de recursos para a manipulação de comum <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Panel> elementos filho.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Windows.Controls.UIElementCollection> has affinity to its own context (class).
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Windows.Controls.UIElementCollection> tem afinidade para seu próprio contexto (classe).

trans-unit.source: You must access the collection from the context of the owning <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Panel>.
trans-unit.target: É necessário acessar a coleção no contexto da posse <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Panel>.
